/>\n<br />\n試過訂錯料<br />\n數漏/錯BQ<br />\n出錯圖俾師傅<br />\n畫錯as-fitted 圖等<br />\n多不勝數<br />\n不過屌屌下就會醒目，正所謂百屌成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916b4a5745028d2899862dcb87ad9d65866e9544","tid":1879580,"uid":244358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:11:02.000Z","msg":"交野之前冷靜d睇清楚<br />\n有時我懶無睇真d諗住快交...<br />\n多數就會發現有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb467215aa82aaea609508cfd9d50a84f0f2154","tid":1879580,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa2af0c478b023c6fa5d65e68ea5704c43da11d2","tid":1879580,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8b2440f717a530ebe42fe170268bed45b9bb9c9","tid":1879580,"uid":56084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"每做一樣野之前check 真d 諗下有冇漏先？ 我自己係咁 起馬唔會有大錯 小錯一定避唔到 點都有"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"但係呢，check極都係比人捉到錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575f23bfb9c4bab68f940c6136eb0dd737612dff","tid":1879580,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:32:42.000Z","msg":"fg正常都會做錯既 mark notes啦"},{"pid":"0d778efbb01ac0ca473e24d0077b38395b712313","tid":1879580,"uid":91693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"有時係懶唔想check<br />\n不過改緊<br />\n原本都多野做，仲要check埋，要用好多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7b28312085366f35703b1c550cc0e5cdbf7fc3","tid":1879580,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d778efbb01ac0ca473e24d0077b38395b712313","tid":1879580,"uid":91693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"有時係懶唔想check<br 